Actress Nnaji Charity has recounted how she ignored chats of gospel Minister, Michael Aworosaiye who committed suicide few days ago in Abuja. Nnaji Charity in her post disclosed that she feels guilty now after she ignored chats of the gospel minister, following reports which revealed that he committed suicide. She wrote in parts; “I really feel guilty of my self right now,,to be honest ” the way we ignore or not respond to chats and calls from our love ones or friends at any point in time is so devastated,,, without knowing what they are passing through at that point of time,, my heart goes to the family of Micheal” the man of God who committed suicide yesterday.” Source